               <title>INACTIVE INGREDIENTS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Colloidal Silicon, Croscarmellose, Sodium, Dicalcium Phosphate, FD&amp;C Blue#1, FD&amp;C Blue#2, Lethicin, Magnesium Stearate, Microcrystalline Cellulose, Polyethylene Glycol, Polyvinyl Alcohol , Titanium Dioxide, Talc.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20231005"/>
